Section 4 
Session 1 - Number types and functions  
  - Always make sure that you are using the right db
  - Not being on the right DB can cause all sorts of context problems
  - To select a db USE db_name
  - When creating a table or db you may need to refresh Object Explorer view
  - Wrong data type declarations will cause compilation errors
